title: Ceiling Paper, 1905–15
description: Alternating large and small floral medallions connected by floral vining and wreaths. Empty medallions in the resulting negative spaces. Ground is very light blue. Printed in yellow, light blue, white, and gold mica.

tombstone.epitaph:
Ceiling Paper, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed on paper. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-1148.
